"      </a>",
"      <br/>",
"      <a class=\"medical medical_basics\" href=\"UTD.htm?30/1/30738?source=see_link\">",
"       Patient information: Normal sexual development (puberty) (The Basics)",
"      </a>",
"     </p>",
